QuestData.Title: False Prophecies
QuestData.Description: Now dat dis nuisance is out of de way, I can return my focus to de city. Zuldazar has languished while I was away.$b$bYou should return to Rastakhan. Let de king know dat his will has been carried out and dat dis false prophet is no more.$b$bYou might think to share Vol'jamba's prophecy with him, if you feel it worth his notice. I cannot say it will change anything at all.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to King Rastakhan at Dazar'alor.
